##User can click on an image to generate a resource
##Users have an up-to-date count of all their resources
##Users have at least 4 upgrades to purchase
##At least 1 click upgrade and 1 automatic upgrade
##Users cannot purchase an upgrade if they do not have the resources
###Purchasing an upgrade decreases the resource immediately
###Upgrades have different modifier values
###When a user buys an upgrade, the price of the upgrade goes up
#####Users can see how many of each upgrade they have and the amount of modification that upgrade provides
####Automatic upgrades are applied at least every 3 seconds, and the screen is updated to reflect this change automatically